\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid1661543\charrsid8421308 Janet:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1661543\charrsid8421308 Not really no.  No.  Wouldn\rquote t say that.  I did go to \'85
 I kept my hand in a bit, I went to seminars at the University \'85 It was a joint Sociology and Anthropology Department, I think.  And so I kept in touch with what was going on in sociology, through that means, to some extent.  I wa
s becoming very involved in the British Sociological Association as well.  But, no, nobody of any particular influence in Hull, no.
