\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid1661543\charrsid8421308 Janet:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1661543\charrsid8421308 
Yes, very much so.  Absolutely, yes.  Yes.  Quite a lot of that, yes.  Yes.  I mean, I didn\rquote t \'85 I don\rquote t think I made a great deal of the concept of grounded theory in this book, but certainly
 that, that approach to research, with which they\rquote re associated, have very much informed quite a lot of the work that I\rquote ve done.
