\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid1661543\charrsid8421308 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid1661543\charrsid8421308 Oh.  Okay.  And would that also be true about your article, \'93It\rquote 
